{"tid":574561,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【改詞】為2018年世界盃外圍賽總結(原曲：家書)","createTime":"2018-02-27T13:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T08:00:43.000Z","uid":37464,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8da13dc27a1e1fbc6ea34a92b4d3b37a3c2d16aa","tid":574561,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EM_KhIEzzmA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEM_KhIEzzmA&d=pEr3Gf3csFW2%2FMgE8lB5IL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=4b5f12aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EM_KhIEzzmA</a><br />\n<br />\n原詞：陳詠謙 <br />\n作曲：張子堅<br />\n填詞：DC_<br />\n<br />\n四年也許太短　匆匆的時光<br />\n假使間略過　會瘋狂<br />\n過程有驚有喜　只可惜地方<br />\n不招呼敗將　更哀傷<br />\n<br />\n一天天過去    一位位告退<br />\n至發覺世界    已翻到新的篇章並未暫停<br />\n<br />\n逝去了的青春　實在代價高昂<br />\n橫越各區海港　奮戰四面八方<br />\n只為了明年世盃可以在場綻放<br />\n誰可算到　現實是被放逐遠方<br />\n<br />\n怎麼講　就像大國消亡<br />\n回望荷蘭這次　<br />\n伴著洛賓身影歸於黑暗埋葬<br />\n若果希丁克那時能捱過<br />\n或者在明年　天清氣朗<br />\n<br />\n有人會因這天    可千秋流芳<br />\n冰島的盛世　已啟航<br />\n過程有得有失　差些少第一<br />\n慘遭到誤判　太冤枉<br />\n<br />\n不屈的國腳　不死的拼搏<br />\n要說對與錯　縱使有清楚死因但是奈何<br />\n<br />\n為了國土的家   就像別國沙拿<br />\n無懼各種風沙   哪怕氣候太差<br />\n不斷拼回來    看卡希爾在場獵殺<br />\n才可印證    席位是用努力競爭<br />\n<br />\n多驚險    亦未及阿根廷<br />\n從後回追到尾    若是萬一失手<br />\n不知怎去回應<br />\n瑞典專心搏鬥才能求勝<br />\n為捲席重來    不失拚勁<br />\n<br />\n只需要    一子錯<br />\n整個局勢    就不可扭轉    身心都受挫<br />\n<br />\n直到領先一刻    亦未預計打和<br />\n隨著幾番失分    最尾智利折返<br />\n巴利再神奇    也因傷勢未能盡興<br />\n環境變了   實力弱亦有力發聲<br />\n<br />\n當指揮   實在是要聰明<br />\n雲杜拿的教訓   讓實力居高者<br />\n輸得只有傻勁<br />\n敗者心聲結尾誰能聆聽<br />\n為出陣球員    衷心致敬"},{"pid":"72d8a6faca0621d41b39a52450dbd2bd63706d46","tid":574561,"uid":37464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"歐國盃2012：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AlHedumuyHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAlHedumuyHg&d=pEr3Gf3csFW2%2FMgE8lB5IL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=63c69007\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AlHedumuyHg</a><br />\n世界盃2014：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LqLo1hrIumo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLqLo1hrIumo&d=pEr3Gf3csFW2%2FMgE8lB5IL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=35de4c95\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LqLo1hrIumo</a><br />\n歐國盃2016：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yRk3on6Z4MY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyRk3on6Z4MY&d=pEr3Gf3csFW2%2FMgE8lB5IL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=557e45cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yRk3on6Z4MY</a>"},{"pid":"77ec3ae5bea10a3d4517dbe61eabf51884bc9718","tid":574561,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T13:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd63b5016ecc21fddc71f301d9a640934f8d886","tid":574561,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"支持!!"},{"pid":"b2071ec4dc19b5990c57766aa34c031484f1e746","tid":574561,"uid":48604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"14世盃個首 4年前聽完 <br />\n依加仲好記得d歌詞<br />\n<br />\n回望這一次世盃 率先一個看點 <br />\n伊巴激戰C朗成預賽經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc383acc5173aaff8270953e8d5706efe280188","tid":574561,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"四年後唱功大躍進"},{"pid":"07200bfc09b945058e91786ddbca3b6c94ca09e1","tid":574561,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bd63b5016ecc21fddc71f301d9a640934f8d886","tid":574561,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"支持!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" 